 for this summer's Paris Olympics have been chosen for their environmental credentials, not to prevent competitors from having sex, organisers said.\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"REUTERS PublishedMay\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"UpdatedMay\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"cardboard\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"the beds\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 442}, {\"ngram\": \"the Athletes' Village\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"their environmental credentials\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"sex\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The clarification came after fresh reports that the beds, manufactured by Japanese company Airweave and already used during the Tokyo 2020 Games, were to deter athletes from jumping under the covers together in the City of Love.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 694, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9994494894246693, \"rank\": 0.00028519412586584727, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The clarification\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh reports\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"the beds\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"Airweave\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 719}