 broad range\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"body types\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"judokas\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fully modular Airweave beds can be customised to accommodate long and large body sizes, with the mattresses - made out of resin fibre - available with different firmness levels.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fully modular Airweave beds\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"long and large body sizes\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"the mattresses\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1735}, {\"ngram\": \"different firmness levels\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the Games, the bed frames will be recycled, while the mattresses and pillows will be donated to schools or associations.\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"the bed frames\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"the mattresses\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"pillows\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"associations\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes will sleep in single beds, two or three to a room, in the Village, a newly built complex close to the main athletics stadium in a northern suburb of the capital.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"single beds\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"a room\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"the Village\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"the main athletics stadium\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2067}, {\"ngram\": \"a northern suburb\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \